{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "sc-aq-30d-iter5",
    "name": "StableCoin-AssetQuality-30d-iter5",
    "description": "APPROACH 3 iter5 — ASSET QUALITY MODEL (6.4): HQLA degradation across 7-instrument portfolio.\n\nPortfolio: $101,000 reserves / $100,000 token supply (1% over-collateral — GENIUS/MiCA)\n  cash-reserve-001:    $12,000  HQLA L1 quality=100  perpetual\n  operating-cash-001:  $11,000  HQLA L1 quality=100  perpetual\n  tbill-4wk-001:       $10,000  HQLA L1 quality=100  matures 2026-03-21 (day 18)\n  tbill-13wk-001:      $32,000  HQLA L1 quality=100  matures 2026-04-21\n  tbill-26wk-001:      $26,000  HQLA L1 quality=100  matures 2026-06-15\n  commpaper-90d-001:    $6,000  HQLA L2A quality=85  matures 2026-04-15\n  defi-yield-001:       $4,000  HQLA L2B quality=60  matures 2026-06-01\n\nQUALITY THRESHOLDS (GENIUS/MiCA):\n  QUALITY_THRESHOLD = 70 (HQLA weighted quality score)\n  bankStressThreshold = 0.50\n  qualityFloor = 70 (vs 50 in stablecoin-1)\n  sovereignMaxDegradation = 0.30\n\n30-DAY LIFECYCLE (iter5 mint→halt→restore mapped to daily cadence):\n  Days 1-3:   Normal — quality=96 (commpaper+defi weight below 100)\n  Days 4-10:  Peg stress begins, bank stress rises — quality degrades\n  Day 11:     BANK STRESS crosses 0.50 — quality enters degradation zone\n  Days 11-18: HALT PERIOD — bank stress 0.55-0.75, defi degrades to 35\n              commpaper quality: 85*(1-bankStress*0.5) → floor ~50\n  Day 18:     tbill-4wk-001 matures — cash injection restores portfolio\n              bank stress begins recovery\n  Days 19-30: Recovery — quality climbs back above 70 threshold\n\nKEY CHANGE vs stablecoin-1:\n  qualityFloor raised to 70 (GENIUS/MiCA compliant minimum)\n  defi-yield-001 quality degrades to 35 during crisis (days 11-18)\n  comm paper stress-adjusted: 85*(1-bankStress*0.5)\n  Weighted quality: (L1*totalL1 + commpaper*adj + defi*adj) / totalMtM\n\nOpen Postman Console (Ctrl+Alt+C) before running.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
